#******************************************************************************
# Makefile<recorder>                                          Recorder project
#******************************************************************************
#
#  File Description:
#
#     The top-level makefile for Recorder, a non-blocking flight recorder
#     for C or C++ programs
#
#
#
#
#
#
#******************************************************************************
# (C) 2015-2018 Christophe de Dinechin <christophe@dinechin.com>
